M Drive DownPST The M drive is currently down Houston is aware of the problem and working to resolve it Right now there is no ETA on when it will be fixed We will keep you updated as soon as we get any information Thanks Diana

M Drive FixedPST The M drive problem has been resolved The Cluster Volume went off line and has been brought back online Please let us know if you have any futher problems Thanks Diana Original Message From Willigerod Diana Sent Thursday June AM To Portland West Desk Subject M Drive Down The M drive is currently down Houston is aware of the problem and working to resolve it Right now there is no ETA on when it will be fixed We will keep you updated as soon as we get any information Thanks Diana

Bloomberg SeminarPST I have been asked to forward on some information from our Bloomberg Sales Rep Kristin Hordyke They are holding a free Energy Seminar on July th pm in the Heathman Hotel You can sign up directly from your Bloomberg Terminal under the Bloomberg University function option Also for those of you who are interested in a training session on the Bloomberg terminals Kristin Hordyke will be in Portland July th and th Please let her know if you are interested in learning more about your Bloomberg Please feel free to contact Kristin with any questions at or email her at Thanks Diana

MAWANELLA Virus AlertPST Please Delete any messages with the subject of MAWANELLA immedately Do not open them We have alerted the Virus team that we are recieving these emails If you have accidentally run the attachment please alert us as soon as possible If you have not run the attachment but opened the mail you are not infected vdescsvbswgzshtml I have attached a URL if you are interested in learning more about this virus Thanks Diana
